data.description: Don't miss this incredibly priced home in North East Lemoore, Ca. 1,672 Sq Ft with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, Newer Vinyl Flooring, Newer AC and Composition Roof( 2015) Newer Windows ( 2019) and Solar panels too ! Step inside and find a tiled entry and vinyl flooring that flows throughout most of the house. There is a dining area that opens to the living area where you will enjoy a fireplace for upcoming winter evenings . A small breakfast nook leads you into the kitchen with tiled flooring. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar for additional seating. All 3 bedrooms are located down the hallway with an ensuite bathroom in the main bedroom. Outdoors is a covered patio and a large backyard for your outdoor projects. This home is priced to sell so don't hesitate to call today !
